  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI just started with Solidity learning and trying Truffle. Unfortunately, I'm not able to solve the error 0308010C\r\n\r\n`Error: error:0308010C:digital envelope routines::unsupported`\r\n\r\nI found that this issue is caused by the latest nodejs and that can be solved with `--openssl-legacy-provider` switch. Unfortunately I'm not able to find out how/where to set it. \r\n\r\nI tried windows environment but without success and I can't find `package.json` where I should set it. \r\n\r\nCan I ask for help with that? I'm c++ dev and nodeJs environment is completely new for me so maybe I'm overlooking something. Thanks\r\n\r\n```\r\nPS Q:\\Solidity\\test01> truffle develop\r\nError: error:0308010C:digital envelope routines::unsupported\r\n    at new Hash (node:internal/crypto/hash:67:19)\r\n    at Object.createHash (node:crypto:130:10)\r\n    at hash160 (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\node_modules\\ethereum-cryptography\\vendor\\hdkey-without-crypto.js:249:1)\r\n    at HDKey.set (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\node_modules\\ethereum-cryptography\\vendor\\hdkey-without-crypto.js:50:1)\r\n    at Function.HDKey.fromMasterSeed (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\node_modules\\ethereum-cryptography\\vendor\\hdkey-without-crypto.js:194:1)\r\n    at Function.EthereumHDKey.fromMasterSeed (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\node_modules\\ethereumjs-wallet\\dist\\hdkey.js:16:1)\r\n    at Object.getAccountsInfo (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\packages\\core\\lib\\mnemonics\\mnemonic.js:45:1)\r\n    at Object.module.exports [as run] (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\packages\\core\\lib\\commands\\develop\\run.js:30:44)\r\n    at Command.run (C:\\Users\\user\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\truffle\\build\\webpack:\\packages\\core\\lib\\command.js:189:1)\r\nTruffle v5.4.25 (core: 5.4.25)\r\nNode v17.3.0\r\n```\r\n\r\nVersions:\r\n\r\n```\r\nNpm 8.3.0\r\nTruffle v5.4.25 (core: 5.4.25)\r\nSolidity - 0.8.4 (solc-js)\r\nNode v17.3.0\r\nWeb3.js v1.5.3\r\n```\r\n\r\nWindows 10\r\nVSCode\r\n\r\n",
