    "body": "Hi @ludekvodicka, unfortunately, Truffle does not support Node 17. Odd node versions are not stable, as they are meant for library maintainers to use to find bugs for the next even (stable) version. You can try downgrading to node 16, though we do not yet officially support it, so it may be necessary or safest to use node 14. Please let us know if you have any issues with this. Thanks!",
