    "body": "Note:\r\n- Truffle unboxing might take some time based on device specs.\r\n- Most importantly give it some time, to download all the dependencies.\r\n- DO NOT INTERRUPT till you see `Unbox successful, sweet!`\r\n- Follow the necessary steps i.e `truffle develop` -> `migrate` -> `open new terminal` -> `cd client`\r\n- First run `npm test` to test if everything is working properly\r\n\r\nATTENTION:\r\n- Make sure the folder containing the truffle box doesn't have any other node_modules in it (learnt it the hard way). This might cause the dependencies to clash.\r\n",
